title.rendered: Salem Spartans vs Chepauk Super Gillies, Match Prediction, Playing XI, Pitch Report

content.rendered:
The Murgan Ashwin led ‘Salem Spartans(SS)’ squad and Kaushik Gandhi led ‘Chepauk Super Gillies (CSG)’ team are set to reunion at Salem cricket Foundation Stadium (SCF) as 22nd Match of TNPL-22 on Tuesday July 19th. Both teams are looking to win anyhow.

The CSG skipper Gandhi’s strategy to increase winning number as a three-match winning streak and against bottom-placed Spartans. CSG’s players also eye for a dominant win and hope to solidify their position at the top as their last 5 match result (W-W-W-L-L). On the other hand Spartan’s will be hoping to register their first win of this season TNPL.

Experts say,

SS batters and bowlers both will put on a good show with their bat and ball as they are seeking to register their first win according to SS last match result (L-L-L-L)

Cricket and pitch report experts Said,

Success never comes without facing failure experiences following this line SS squad would come at SCF ground in Salem District for their first win. SS players will also get advantage of their home district pitch as they have more experience than CSG’s players at venue.

Pitch Report: SS vs CSG

Salem cricket Foundation Stadium (SCF), Salem district

The pitch at SCF Ground, Salem is a well-balanced pitch, but according to pitch experts this is pro batting pitch in first inning of match. If batter have earlier experience about the pitch then they can perform good in second inning also, but it depends upon their batting experiences at venue. The SS and CSG both are likely to score 150+ if they bat in first inning.

An overview of last matches result

  • SS last four match-     (L-L-L-L)
  • CSG last five match-  (W-W-W-L-L)

(L= Lose, W= Win)

SS and CSG Probable Squad

SS : Gopinath, R Kavin, S Ganesh, Daryl Ferrario, Jafar Jamal, Ravi Karthikeyan, Murugan Ashwin(C), S Abhishek, G Kishoor, G Periyaswamy, M Ganesh Moorthi

CSG: Kaushik Gandhi(C), N Jagadeeshan, Uthirasamy Sasidev, Sonu Yadav, Rajagopal Sathish, S Harish Kumar, Sai Kishore, S Radhakrishnan, Manimaran Siddharth, R Alexander, Sandeep Warrier

SS vs CSG Match Details:

Today, 19 July

Timing: 7:15PM

Venue: Salem Cricket Foundation Stadium(SCF), Salem

22nd match of TNPL-2022.

Prediction- SS is likely to win as per these below three grounds- (i) SS players have big experiences at SCF ground as their home district ground.

(ii) SS players have solid hunger to register their first win of League.

(iii) SS players will get advantage of CSG’s poor performance in their last two matches.

Read Also: Taj777 News is the associate sponsor of Salem Spartans in TNPL 2022
